<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/Home.css" asp-append-version="true" />
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1> ABC RETAIL</h1>
            <p>We believe that fashion should be as dynamic and versatile as the city itself. Our curated collection blends cutting-edge style with unparalleled comfort, offering you the perfect wardrobe essentials for every aspect of urban living.</p>
            <a href="#explore" class="btn btn-hero">Explore Our Collection</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="grid-container">

        <article class="featured">
            <img src="~/Pic/Graphic Tees.jpg" alt="Our Team Image" class="section-image">
            <div>
                <h2>
                    Graphic Tees

                </h2>
                <p>
                    Trendy and comfortable tees featuring unique designs and bold prints that add a touch of personality to any casual outfit.

                </p>
                <a href="https://www.timeout.com/arts-and-culture/best-quotes-about-art-by-famous-artists" class="btn btn1">Read More</a>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article>
            <img src="~/Pic/Sustainable Activewear.jpg" alt="Our Story Image" class="section-image">
            <div>
                <h3>Sustainable Activewear</h3>
                <p> High-performance activewear made from eco-friendly materials, including leggings, sports bras, and workout tops designed for both style and function.</p>
                <a href="https://www.timeout.com/arts-and-culture/best-quotes-about-art-by-famous-artists" class="btn btn1">Read More</a>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article>
            <img src="~/Pic/Tailored Blazers.jpg" alt="Our Mission Image" class="section-image">
            <div>
                <h3>Tailored Blazers</h3>
                <p>Stylish blazers that offer a sophisticated look for both professional and semi-formal occasions, available in various colors and fits.</p>
                <a href="https://www.timeout.com/arts-and-culture/best-quotes-about-art-by-famous-artists" class="btn btn1">Read More</a>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article>
            <img src="~/Pic/Chic Statement Dresses.jpg" alt="Our Values Image" class="section-image">
            <div>
                <h3>Chic Statement Dresses</h3>
                <p>Eye-catching dresses designed for special events or nights out, featuring modern cuts, vibrant colors, and unique patterns.</p>
                <a href="https://www.timeout.com/arts-and-culture/best-quotes-about-art-by-famous-artists" class="btn btn1">Read More</a>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article>
            <img src="~/Pic/Elegant Jewelry.jpg" alt="Our Values Image" class="section-image">
            <div>
                <h3>Elegant Jewelry</h3>
                <p>A selection of statement necklaces, bracelets, and earrings crafted to enhance both everyday and formal outfits with a touch of elegance.</p>
                <a href="https://www.timeout.com/arts-and-culture/best-quotes-about-art-by-famous-artists" class="btn btn1">Read More</a>
            </div>
        </article>


        <article>
            <img src="~/Pic/Versatile Sneakers.png" alt="Our Values Image" class="section-image">
            <div>
                <h3>Versatile Sneakers</h3>
                <p>
                    Fashionable and comfortable sneakers suitable for a variety of activities, available in multiple styles and colors to match any look.
                </p>
                <a href="https://www.timeout.com/arts-and-culture/best-quotes-about-art-by-famous-artists" class="btn btn1">Read More</a>
            </div>


        </article>

    </main>

    <!-- Testimonials Section -->
    <section class="testimonials">
        <h2>What Our Customers Say</h2>
        <div class="testimonial-grid">
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"ABC Retail has transformed my wardrobe! Their pieces are both stylish and incredibly comfortable."</p>
                <h4>- Emily Johnson</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"I love the blend of fashion and functionality. Every item I’ve bought is perfect for my busy city life!"</p>
                <h4>- Michael Lee</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"Their sustainable fashion line is fantastic. I feel good about my purchases and love the stylish designs."</p>
                <h4>- Sarah Miller</h4>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer Section -->


</body>
</html>



